item.title: Home
item.dc:creator: a_6514361
item.content:encoded: DNA BioMed specializes in providing international companies with import/distribution service, innovative and cost-effective solutions to laboratories throughout the globe. Our unique, client-focused approach allows us to deliver quality products specifically tailored to meet the needs of worldwide medical community. We pride ourselves on listening to our clients' input and designing solutions customized to meet their demands. Through scientific knowledge and experience, maintaining excellent business relationships, and emphasizing quality, value-driven service to our clients, we strive to meet the needs of our customers wherever, whenever, and however we can.

item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: a_6514361
item.content:encoded:
Since the establishment of DNA BioMed in 2004, one goal remains foremost in our mind - to be able to introduce our clients to the most significant, efficient and affordable products available that will allow them to maximize their laboratories' potential.

Our mission is to become the leader in assisting clients with introducing and delivering their innovative and advanced products to the worldwide medical community.  Our management team possesses strong medical, legal, regulatory, business, marketing knowledge and experience, and can provide services to our customers in branding their product, market submission and import/export distribution.  

Laboratories today are faced with the difficult challenge of handling increased volume while reducing costs to meet the demands of a money-conscious market. In order for clinical laboratories to remain competitive, they must find a way to increase their productivity while operating within a tight budget. The solution - laboratory automation!

Automation allows laboratories to streamline their workflow and reduce bottlenecks in the pre- and post-analytical phases. It also produces faster, more reliable results in the analytical phase. With the assistance of automation, laboratories can dramatically reduce the costs of errors and labor while increasing throughput and decreasing turnaround time.

Automated solutions allow laboratories to provide patients with faster, more reliable results, improve physician satisfaction and increase their capacity while maintaining a cost-effective environment. As a result, they remain competitive in today’s marketplace.

With our client needs in mind, the management and sales teams at DNA BioMed seek worldwide relationships that will bring quality, cutting-edge products. DNA BioMed is committed to providing our customers with cost-effective solutions that will solve the unique problems that each laboratory faces. In order to reach this goal, our current product line can be customized to meet the individual needs of each laboratory. This focus and dedication to the specialized needs of each customer has resulted in significant interest and demand for our products and services nationwide.

We are excited about working with you to find a customized solution to your laboratory's needs that will work to improve your efficiency, increase your throughput and reduce your costs.

item.title: Services
item.dc:creator: a_6514361
item.content:encoded:
DNA BioMed understands that our customers rely upon us to provide support services to maximize system uptime and
increase their efficiency. That is why DNA BioMed provides full customer support services with 24-hour telephone
troubleshooting, on-site service and extensive customer training. Through initial education and ongoing consultation, our aim
is to provide our clients with the greatest understanding of their specialized product. The service team at DNA BioMed is trained directly by the equipment manufacturers on the effective operation and maintenance of each and every product it
offers. We make it our duty to provide quality education and support so that our customers can realize maximum benefits
from DNA BioMed's products.

24-Hour Telephone Troubleshooting and On-Site Customer Support

For assistance with our products, please call (240) 290-0079. We have friendly service personnel ready to answer your
questions any time - day or night.

If we are unable to answer your questions over the phone, a service technician will be dispatched to your site to complete
any necessary troubleshooting and repairs.

E-mail Support Services

If you would like electronic assistance with any of our products, please email service@dnabiomed.com and one of our
service representatives will respond during normal business hours.

If you need immediate assistance, please call our 24-hour telephone troubleshooting line.

On-Site Training

When we place one of our products in your laboratory, we provide extensive training on maintenance procedures and
basic repairs. We believe that first-hand knowledge of equipment operators is essential to successful utilization of our
products and will help to educate our customers to fully understand their purchases.

item.title: Health Screening
item.dc:creator: a_6514361
item.content:encoded:
What is preventive health screening? 

Preventive health screenings help people understand their risk for developing chronic conditions before symptoms are present, while they can still take action.  DNA BioMed is excited to partner with Fu Jing Catholic Hospital with its brand new state of the art facility in Taiwan.  The non-invasive screenings provided by Fu Jing Catholic Hospital Screening identify risk factors that can lead to cardiovascular disease, stroke, cancer, peripheral artery disease, osteoporosis, and other serious illnesses. These health screening services, combined with the ongoing medical care provided by a personal physician, are designed to keep people independent and active for as long as possible.
